	Scarlett bubbly    
	 London, April 2: Hollywood actress Scarlett Johansson has been photographed in a series of publicity shots as the new face of champagne firm Moet amp; Chandon, reports The Daily Telegraph.      
	The 24-year-old posed in a series of provocative images, including one in which she holds a champagne glass between her toes.      
	 another photograph she lounges beside a swimming pool dressed in high heels and a gold dress while scooping ice from an ice bucket. The campaign was shot by photographers Mert Alas and Marcus Piggott.      
	Speaking in London last month, Johansson said: I am honoured to have been chosen as their ambassador and to make history with the brand.
                                                                                                                                                                       
